<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٨ - <span class="c2">(١٨١٥)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1199">حَاتِمٌ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ أَنَّهُ قَالَ فِي كِلْتَيْهِمَا:</span> سَبْعَ غَزَوَاتٍ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>